NARRATIVE TAGS & LEGACY
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
• [DEBTOR – 67,342¥]
  Origin: Character creation, Session 0
  Domain: Material / Moral
  Weight: High
  Effect: Nakamura owns your SIN. Interest compounds daily.
  Legacy: You are not free. No one is.

• [PROMISED]
  Origin: Session 1 – The Container
  Domain: Metaphysical / Moral
  Weight: High
  Effect: You gave Hana your word. You will return and tell her what you found.
  Legacy: The container remembers. Forty years of waiting recognized you.

• [SISTER-CHOSEN]
  Origin: Session 1 – Mira
  Domain: Relational
  Weight: High
  Effect: Mira chose you. She doesn't know your name. She holds your hand anyway.
  Legacy: Some families are made, not born.

• [THE MAN WITH MILITARY HANDS]
  Origin: Session 1 – Dock encounter
  Domain: [UNCLEAR ORIGIN]
  Weight: Medium
  Effect: He worked for Emiko. He named his daughter after her. He gave you the chip.
  Legacy: Not all debts are measured in nuyen.

• [EMIKO'S DAUGHTER]
  Origin: Session 1 – The Man's testimony
  Domain: Relational / Legacy
  Weight: Medium
  Effect: Emiko (daughter), age 37, deceased 2075, leukemia.
  Legacy: He named her after the woman he was paid to protect.

